MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2006-1284. State v. Troglin.

Union App. No. 14-05-56, 2006-Ohio-2791. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
